### Audit System Test Requests

@gatewayUrl = https://localhost:7034
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Get Audit Statistics
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Recent Audit Logs (Last 24 hours)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/recent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get My Audit Logs (Current User)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/my-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get User Audit Logs
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/user/user123?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Entity Audit Logs (Suppliers)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/entity/Supplier?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Entity Audit Logs (Specific Supplier)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/entity/Supplier?entityId=1&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Audit Logs by Date Range
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/date-range?startDate=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&endDate=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z&page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Audit Logs by Action (LOGIN)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/action/LOGIN?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Audit Logs by Action (CREATE)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/action/CREATE?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Audit Logs by Action (UPDATE)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/action/UPDATE?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Audit Logs by Action (DELETE)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/action/DELETE?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Specific Audit Log by ID
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete Audit Log (SuperAdmin only)
DELETE {{gatewayUrl}}/api/audit/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test Login (This will create an audit log)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/api/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

